response.original_title: Berlin mit der S-Bahn erfahren: Geschichte und Geschichten entlang der S1
response.overview: S-Bahn line 1 extends from Berlin's southwest to the north, from Wannsee to Oranienburg. There are many sights along the route and history from divided to reunified Berlin can also be experienced here. The film tells of places and people along the S-Bahn line.
response.title: Berlin mit der S-Bahn erfahren: Geschichte und Geschichten entlang der S1
